Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.05,0:00:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it true that a Navy ship came?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A Navy ship did?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard that it was\Nanchored here when day broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the Navy come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to such a remote island?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one has seen any marines on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a single person can be found.\NIt's like a ghost ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Professor!\N--Professor Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's nothing to worry about,\Nbut a Navy ship is anchored at the seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might be here for an investigation.\NWe should be cautious, just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the scholars know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raft is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:01:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You've got\N"I'm lonely" written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I was thinking\Nof attaching a flag or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To sea? So you wanna set out to sea, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom has been busy with her\Narchaeological research all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she comes back\Nto this island next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask her to take me with her to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I studied hard and I was finally\Nable to become an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An archaeologist? When you're still so small?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... you don't even remember\Nyour mom's face, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... but she's still my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, Saul...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that the world has a blank history\Nof 100 years that no one knows about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's called the "Blank Century."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about it, but the Government\Nprohibits people from investigating, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.17,0:02:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I heard that my mom is traveling\Naround the world investigating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't tell anyone about it,\Nsince it's actually a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it mean that she's traveling in\Nsearch of those stones called Poneglyphs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about Poneglyphs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do! But don't talk\Nabout it in front of people, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, about your\Nmom traveling in search of... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin... Do you know your mom's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:03:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nico Olvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin is Olvia's daughter...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... could this place be...\Nan island called Ohara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Ahh! This is terrible! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I drifted to Ohara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be sitting around talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin!\N--What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might shock you, but listen to me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy battleships should be\Nheaded to Ohara right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to eliminate the scholars on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's a lie...\N--Don't tell the Government you're a scholar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's a lie...!\N--Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! I'd never lie to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to town now and see if anything\Nstrange has been happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible your mom might be back, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:14.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:24.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cross this endless sea to go in search of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:30.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a global miracle no one\Nhas yet been able to find
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:35.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our hearts pounding,\Nwe'll just charge ahead as we please
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:42.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,following the footprints of\Nthose who chase their dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:48.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stormy the night,\Nif we join our hearts as one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:52.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we will be able to make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:05:00.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nholding our flag high in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:06.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there are tears\Nwe don't want anyone to see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:12.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Nif we want to achieve our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:15.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,we should always look\Nstraight ahead without fear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:24.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:30.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Get running, get running,\Nhead past everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:36.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we don't run from it,\Nwe can grasp tomorrow in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:42.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase it, chase it,\Neverything we see before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:47.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's carve it into the blank pages of our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Brand New World
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:58.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fated Mother and Daughter!\NThe Mother's Name Is Olvia!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Olvia...\N--Olvia-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you who came on that Navy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you had been caught by the Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I came back bearing bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I just said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the government has finally\Nset its sights on Ohara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Poneglyph search team that set off\Nfrom Ohara six years ago was annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them except for me...\NA total of 33 members...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also temporarily captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government evaluated\Nmy fellow scholars' belongings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and figured out that we came from Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is inexcusable! To think that this\Nisland is now in danger because of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! It's no one's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who set out to sea and those\Nwho stayed here--we're all one team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you guys who experienced a terrible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put you through a terrible ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara is a place where talented\Nscholars from all around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gather and continue to study history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government has been\Nconsidering us a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be thinking that they\Nfinally found something on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna pass up this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but we were able to get\Nthat information without delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, everyone in Ohara who\Nclaims to be a scholar will be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone, get out of Ohara immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... This time, we probably won't\Nbe able to slip past their investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like we usually do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if they are trying to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, hurry up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Olvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run away leaving this\Ntreasure of mankind behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We feel the same way, Olvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what the Government is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we run, the precious history\Nthat exists here won't be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll try whatever we can,\Njust like we always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there must be something\Nweighing on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up your mind, Olvia! Are you\Ngonna come aboard the ship or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a lingering attachment\Nto your child, don't come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about your husband's\Nunfinished business, we will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a scholar from Ohara. I can't\Nabandon our predecessors' will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:09:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll solve all the mysteries\Nand come back for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy... Where's Mommy?\NWhere did Mommy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom set out to sea for work.\NYou'll stay here with us for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're noisy! Be quiet or I'll hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it. She's only two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our daughter is two, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether she's your\Nbig sister's child or whatever--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how dare you take in such a burden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... I... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wanna read books, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have money, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to pay.\NYou can read them all for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Free?\N--Yeah, since this is the best library in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The best one in the world?\N--That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're Olvia's daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like books?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks just like you did\Nwhen you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And like you were at that age,\Nshe's a rare genius, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I know she's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stepped into this line of work.\NSo I have to give up my attachment to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I can't make her a "criminal's daughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Clover! This time, a ship flying\Nthe World Government's flag has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Government ship has come\Nall the way to the West Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It indeed seems quite serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys and I are neither fellow\Nscholars nor acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind... no matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Olvia! What're you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let the headquarters know\Nthat we arrived at our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go, go, go! Keep on moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this work'd\Nbetter get me a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, go get all the scholars and restrain them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's going on?!\N--A woman with a gun is running around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Heaven's sake! I'm sorry, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been notified that CP9's\NChief Spandine has arrived in Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that something so important\Nthat you had to wake me up to tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did my mom come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying? There's no way\Nthat your mother is in Ohara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to give up my attachment to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I can't make her a "criminal's daughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Navy battleships\Nare coming to this island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to capture all\Nthe scholars on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a disturbance or\Nsomething happening in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that a Government\Nship just came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:13:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be a more\Nrigorous investigation than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Robin. Even if the\NGovernment people come,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't tell them you're an\Narchaeologist no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're small, no one will think\Nthat you're a scholar. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop what you're doing!\NGet outside with your hands in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being quite violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ohara lab is suspected of a\Nserious crime--deciphering Poneglyphs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It requires a thorough search,\Nso all of you, go outside immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat this place with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The value of everything in here\Nis beyond your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to listen to what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all the townspeople!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now suspect that this island's scholars\Nare devils who wish to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're world-class scholars\Nand the pride of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consequently, we'll conduct a\Nlarge-scale search of the entire island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, those who have\Nnothing to do with archaeology
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are expected to take an ID with them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and temporarily take refuge on the\Nevacuation ship at the west seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An evacuation ship?!\NWhy are you going that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the scholars' problem,\Nwe have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there should be no need\Nfor us to leave the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our duty to pass that message to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens later\Nto those who ignore our advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's none of our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Leave town!\N--Evacuate to the west seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government is up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! I got shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is it for me! I'm a goner, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the top... that I want my son\Nto take over the position of chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, please take a close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet just went through\Nthe sleeve of your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't miss next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... To think that a heinous\Ncriminal who splendidly escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy's prison is coincidentally\Nvisiting this island... Nico Olvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept denying your connection to\Nthe Ohara scholars, and yet, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as if you're declaring\Nthat this is your hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the scholars here are committing\Nthe same crime that you guys were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My being here alone isn't proof of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have all sorts of\Nexcuses ready. You're a smart woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your connection to Ohara\Ndoesn't need to be proved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we dig through every nook and corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,evidence of your research on\NPoneglyphs will turn up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government thinks that\Nthe probability of this is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to capture you guys,\Nwho were on the run for six long years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just gave the Government a small push.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of Poneglyph\Nresearchers around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time we captured one, we always\Nsearched for their connection to Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... In order to\Nuse Ohara as a warning...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! If Ohara, the holy land\Nof archaeology, is crushed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll send shockwaves throughout academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make the world realize
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what happens to those who\Nresearch the "Blank Century."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the battleships from Headquarters\Nunder standby order are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... Just how much do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're used to ensure that not\Neven a single criminal escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a matter of form,\Nwe need to verify the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're not pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came all the way here to conduct\Na compulsory investigation on the island
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to send off those who have\Nnothing to do with the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it! The books\Nhere are a world treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still someone here? Take him outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come!\N--Dammit, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a hidden room!\NMake sure we find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battleships are already within sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, gather all the scholars here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. The scholars have been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth did they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that the goal of the scholars'\Nresearch is to destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the evacuation ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's at the west seashore! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go! Hurry to the west seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:18:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin... It seems that\Nthere's an evacuation ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer tell what\Nthe Government will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurry up and go there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Even if I get on that ship,\Nthere won't be nice people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin...\N--Just like you guys, I'm a--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys working hard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking the\Ntrouble to come here, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I didn't expect that a ferocious\Nanimal would appear on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nearly killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, listen carefully.\NThis woman is an escaped prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The group she belonged to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was recently eliminated for the crime\Nof deciphering the ancient texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we still don't know the ringleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you guys are connected to this woman,\Nit'll make matters quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible of them to hurt a woman like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, go to the evacuation ship. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...grown so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What have they done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they no respect for the library?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that they'd take\Nsuch drastic measures...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... They've made a big show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Click.\N--Hello? Is this the Chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a secret room in the basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in there, we found a huge stone\Nthat's probably a Poneglyph
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and research documents clearly\Ndiscussing the ancient texts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, scholars of Ohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your death sentence has now been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed regrettable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the world's best archaeologists\Nlose their lives together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? What a letdown. That was all I had to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I have left to do is\Nreport this to the Five Elder Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! Are they really gonna\Nkill all of you?! That's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they do that just because\Nyou read the ancient texts...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You brat! The purpose of their\Nresearch is to revive a powerful weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and commit mass murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! They aren't\Nthinking about anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, stop it. It's pointless to discuss\Nthe matter with an errand boy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really the weapon itself that\Nthe Government is afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Professor!\N--Professor Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's connected, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is good timing.\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me speak to the Five Elder Stars,\Nthe world's leaders, before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the scholars at Ohara, have continued\Nour research for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and although the research isn't completed yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we formed a hypothesis\Nabout the "Blank Century."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like to report it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rubbish...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, get out of here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listening to what I'm about to say is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it seems like the scholars\Nhave been found guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Navy battleships are moving\Ntoward here from the eastern sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna do something!\NLet's hurry to the evacuation ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape from this island right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:03.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:07.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:11.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:15.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll become No. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll aim for freedom in wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:21.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a faint light\Nshowing us the road to tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:23.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,an era created by risking everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:25.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We always try our best, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:27.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to achieve glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:29.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the time--don't be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:31.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll surely win the future\Ntogether with friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:35.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we start running faster\Ntowards the vast world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:39.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take off with unknown powers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:41.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't fear, and we don't waver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:45.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Nin the end we'll surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:49.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We fight harder against\Nthe wall that confronts us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:53.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We charge ahead stronger\Nwith overflowing power
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:57.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't fear even if we\Nhave to give up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:22:59.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:01.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start running towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:09.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's all to ensure we smile in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saul, please take care of Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let my daughter\Nescape from here at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What about you, Mom?!\NAren't you gonna come with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something\Nthat I have to do here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't wanna be separated!\NI was finally able to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Tragedy of Ohara!\NThe Terror of Buster Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
